382
00:24:02,437 --> 00:24:04,737
<i>(Lee)</i>
<i>Yes indeed! I have sent</i>
<i>in a few requests myself!</i>

383
00:24:04,771 --> 00:24:06,371
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Yeah, me too!</i>

384
00:24:06,404 --> 00:24:08,771
<i>(Kakashi)</i>
<i>I send the producers a</i>
<i>crate a week, sometimes two!</i>

385
00:24:08,804 --> 00:24:11,504
<i>(tenten)</i>
<i>You, too, Kakashi Sensei?!</i>

386
00:24:11,537 --> 00:24:14,371
<i>(Tenten)</i>
<i>Man, I swear you</i>
<i>men are all alike!</i>

